_sText: GG_NATAL BY UNREALxmas The map takes place in a little village, it is a Gun Game, but can also be played as a Bomb/defusal map since it has two bombsites and buyzones. This map features: -> 3d skybox -> Falling snow -> Custom materials -> Custom models (Mr. Kit's) -> Soundscapes -> FPSB related -> Christmas related -> A few banana bunches lol :D I optimized the map maximum I could, keeping it detailed and balanced. This map was made for the FPSB's Xmas Levels 2008 Contest. My first contest! Nav. File uploaded. Thanks to Chizbone :D
